These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
House: colonial, victorian
1. the colonial house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is not to the right of the victorian house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| House   | victorian | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold
1. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
2. the person who growstulip is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Flower   | marigold | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, camping
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby   | gardening | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
