.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-6::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, rock
1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of rock is not to the left of the fan of rock##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | rock |

